Photo Technique - January/February 2013 (True PDF)

PHOTO Technique is a photography magazine written for the serious amateur and those working in professional photography who want to create the best possible photographs and images. Bimonthly articles provide techniques on photo shooting and photo printing for traditional photography and digital photography.
